---
---

<section
  style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;text-align:center;padding:4.5rem 1.5rem 5rem;min-height:calc(100vh - 56px);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"
>
  <!-- Hero content -->
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:700px;width:100%;">
    <!-- Eyebrow -->
    <div class="fade-in" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      <span style="font-family:'Jost',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c9a84c;">CardHabit</span>
      <div style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:#c9a84c;"></div>
      <span style="font-family:'Jost',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c9a84c;">Available now</span>
      <div style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:#c9a84c;"></div>
      <span style="font-family:'Jost',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c9a84c;">iOS</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Kicker: the emotional hook, kept as a styled line above the H1 -->
    <p
      class="fade-in"
      style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(1.2rem,3.5vw,1.75rem);line-height:1.2;color:#c9a84c;margin:0 0 0.75rem;"
    >
      Show up. Every day.
    </p>

    <!-- H1: brand + mechanic -->
    <h1
      class="fade-in"
      style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(2.2rem,7.5vw,4rem);line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-0.015em;color:#f0ebe0;margin:0 0 1.75rem;"
    >
      CardHabit deals you five habit cards <em style="color:#c9a84c;font-style:italic;">every morning.</em>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subhead: canonical entity sentence first, then the thesis -->
    <p
      class="fade-in"
      style="font-family:'Jost',system-ui,sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.65;color:#a39e92;max-width:580px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;"
    >
      CardHabit is an iOS daily challenge app that deals you five habit cards each morning, built on trading-card-game mechanics. Hard things every day. Not extreme things, once. You commit to what you can hold, and friends who believe you can handle harder play Challenge cards into your day. Forty days to your archetype.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="fade-in">
      <a
        href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/cardhabit-tcg-habit-tracker/id6768107296"
        class="hero-cta"
        data-appstore-cta="hero"
        style="display:inline-block;background:#c9a84c;color:#0c0c0e;font-family:'Jost',system-ui,sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:1rem 2.25rem;border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.2s,transform 0.2s;border:1px solid #c9a84c;"
      >
        Download on the App Store
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Below CTA note -->
    <p
      class="fade-in"
      style="font-family:'Jost',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#6b6760;margin-top:1.25rem;"
    >
      Free to start &nbsp;·&nbsp; Founder pricing, live in the app now
    </p>

    <!-- The product itself: today's hand on the table -->
    <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top:3rem;display:flex;justify-content:center;">
      <img
        src="/app/home-table.png"
        alt="CardHabit home screen: today's hand of habit cards on the table, two completed and sealed"
        width="300"
        loading="eager"
        style="width:min(300px,72vw);border-radius:32px;border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 60px rgba(201,168,76,0.08);display:block;"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-cta:hover {
    background: #d9b86b;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
</style>
